This index breaks the Mermaid supply-chain diagram into explorable linked tiddlers.

See also: [[AI Supply Chain Mermaid Diagram]] and [[AI Supply Chain Flowchart]].

!! Demand / End Markets
* [[Users / Enterprises / Governments|AI Supply Chain: Users / Enterprises / Governments]] — End customers and institutions whose demand pulls the rest of the AI stack into existence.
